<Date>Fri Feb 06 00:00:00 CST 2004
<Content>What's going on Creative Labs?  Is it a coincidence that I no longer can get any of your Nomad Zen Xtras (worst name ever) at Best Buy and now the 60GB Nomad Xtra is "sold out" or more likely "discontinued" at the almighty Amazon.com? hmmmmm....  
